{
  "chapter": 201,
  "chapter_summary": "第二百零一章 霸刀岳山\n\n本章以洛阳城为背景，讲述了寇仲与宋玉致之间复杂的情感纠葛，以及徐子陵假扮\"霸刀\"岳山与郑石如的遭遇。寇仲在宋玉致处过夜后，两人因感情问题发生争执，宋玉致拒绝了寇仲的追求，令他心痛不已。徐子陵戴着面具在城中行走，被\"河南狂士\"郑石如认出是假扮的\"霸刀\"岳山，郑石如对这位四十年前名震陕北的高手心存敬畏，试图招揽。寇仲在福成绸缎庄偶遇郑淑明和白清儿，双方发生言语冲突。徐子陵最终换上\"刀疤大侠\"面具，继续在城中活动。本章展现了人物之间的情感张力和江湖恩怨，为后续剧情发展埋下伏笔。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "睡够了吗？还不滚起来！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "三小姐拉我起来好吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你若再胡闹，我便把你掷到门外去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "轻点打不行吗？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "无赖！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "三小姐昨夜仗义收留的大恩大德，我寇仲差点便永志不忘。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "什么差点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "若三小姐肯以自己的香闺招待我，那就真的永志不忘。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你为何不避？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我令三小姐这么气恼，理该受罚的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你究竟是怎样的人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "三小姐除非是心甘情愿嫁我，否则我绝不会逼你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "既是如此，你以后就不要再在玉致眼前出现好了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "三小姐若有此意，我寇仲定必遵从。唉！想不到竟是我自作多情，真个好笑！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你心里根本没有我，还说甚么自作多情，再说我便杀了你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我心里怎会没有你？昨晚我还梦见在三小姐的香闺内和三小姐，嘿！那真是个令小弟毕生难忘的美梦。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "狗口长不出象牙的大无赖，占人家的便宜还占得不够吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "昨晚确是占了三小姐颇大的便宜，那是人世间最香甜的美事。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "我敢向着苍天打报告，寇仲心里绝对有宋玉致。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然有啦！因为我是你去争天下的其中一块踏脚石嘛。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "起始时我确是带点功利之心。但到昨晚，我才发觉自己难以自拔的想着玉致你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "宋玉致",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你须谨记大丈夫言出如山，你刚才答应了以后再不会来烦玉致，现在怎能反悔？我不理你是真心还是假意，总之我的心无法把你容纳，言尽于此，你走吧！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "玉致珍重！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这位老丈，可否借一步说话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "老夫没有兴趣和任何人说话，给我滚开。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "这叫敬酒不喝喝罚酒，让郑某人看你有多大道行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "止步！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "老夫已有数十年没动刀子杀人，你最好不要迫老夫破戒。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "老丈高姓大名？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "text": "你明知老夫不会说出姓名，仍要出口相问，岂非多馀之极。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "不用你说出来，我郑石如也猜出你的身份，四十年前名震陕北的'霸刀'岳山，何时变得如此藏头露尾了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shi_ru",
      "speaker_name": "郑石如",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "岳老师今趟出山，当是要一雪前耻，但现在时势已变，个人之力实难展抱负，岳老师请三思，石如稍后再拜会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_fu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "李福成",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是正宗的鲁锦，特别在织造前须预先染色，故色泽多而鲜艳，图案变化万端。由打棉、捻布芯、纺线、染色、上浆、络线、经纱、穿综、上机织布、整理，到最后的严格检验，所有工序一丝不苟。我现在手上这幅唤作万人迷，若……咦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_fu_cheng",
      "text": "我不要女人穿的万人迷，只要一套现成的男装，另加一对马靴，这里若没有就给我到别处弄回来，我当照付双倍价钱。唉！真难受！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "郑淑明",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲是你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_fu_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "李福成",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "原来是寇爷，失敬失敬，尚书大人是福成的老朋友，请到里面坐下先喝口热茶，一切自会为寇爷办得妥妥贴贴。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_fu_cheng",
      "text": "待我先和老朋友交待两句，老板要不要为我量度尺寸，小弟比较欢喜较松身的衣里，哈！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shu_ming",
      "text": "小弟并非跋锋寒，那样瞪着我干吗？淑女和君子同级，所以君子动口时，淑女也不可动手。迟些我订桌酒席向女当家赔罪好吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_qing_er",
      "speaker_name": "白清儿",
      "listener": "char_zheng_shu_ming",
      "text": "姐姐不要睬他，我们到别处玩儿，眼不见为净。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_bai_qing_er",
      "text": "彼此彼此，别忘了通知涫妖女，早晚我定会旧恨新仇一并跟她算账。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_qing_er",
      "speaker_name": "白清儿",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我根本不知你在说甚么，我们走。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zheng_shu_ming",
      "speaker_name": "郑淑明",
      "listener": "char_bai_qing_er",
      "text": "甚么涫妖女？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了阴癸派的妖女外，那里还有妖女呢？哈！唉！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 201,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    }
  ],
